            . I am watch-house-keeper, and received him with the tools - I found a square and apron in his pocket - he said they belonged to the tools.</p>
               <p>THOMAS HASELGROVE. I am a <rs id="t18270712-163-viclabel900" type="occupation">carpenter</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270712-163-victim876 t18270712-163-viclabel900"></join>. This plane and some other tools are mine - I had left them in a new house in <placeName id="t18270712-163-crimeloc901">Liverpool-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18270712-163-crimeloc901" type="placeName" value="Liverpool-street"></interp>
